2.  Poverty<br>
3.  Lack of Education<br>
4.  Oil<br>
<br>
Very few of them are directly traceable to Islam.  The only reason it seems that way is because the majority of the people in this region are Muslim and because this is the only thing that generates ratings and is therefore shown on CNN. <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-size:xx-small;"><br>
